 Palos Verdes Estates 
</P>
<P>
 * The cartoon showing a section of the infamous Nuremberg laws with the word 
"Jew" replaced by "immigrant" was right on target. Prop. 187 was the closest 
thing the world has seen to Nuremberg laws since 1939. 
</P>
<P>
