Coast (4-0). 
</P>
<P>
 In nonconference women's basketball: 
</P>
<P>
 Cypress 72, Grossmont 70 -- Jackie Boxley made a free-throw with four seconds 
to play to close the victory for Cypress (3-1). Sara Works scored 28 points and 
Stephanie Werdel had 24, tying a school record with seven three-point baskets. 
</P>
<P>
 Rancho Santiago 57, Victor Valley 50 -- Lisa Petronis and Grace Cervantes each 
scored 14 points for Rancho Santiago (4-1). Petronis also had 12 rebounds. 
