 In nonconference men's basketball: 
</P>
<P>
 Claremont-Mudd 86, Chapman 72 -- Kevin Zitar scored 23 and former Laguna Beach 
standout Darren Gravley 18 for Claremont, which led by 30 at one point in the 
second half. Adam Dzierzynski and Ramin Bastani each scored 18 points for the 
visiting Panthers (0-1). 
</P>
<P>
 In nonconference women's basketball: 
</P>
<P>
 Chapman 66, Redlands 60 -- Melody Earle scored 14 points and Faye Cruz and 
Alana Conyers each scored 13 for the host Panthers (1-0). 
</P>
<P>
 In nonconference volleyball: 
</P>
<P>
 Colorado State 3, UC Irvine 2 -- Meredith Fletcher set a school record of 69 
assists in UC Irvine's loss to Colorado State, 12-15, 15-12, 18-16, 13-15, 
15-8. The former record of 66 was set by Vesna Sepic last year. 
</P>
