</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Durell Price 
</P>
<P>
 SCHOOL: Sylmar 
</P>
<P>
 SPORT: Football 
</P>
<P>
 YEAR: Junior 
</P>
<P>
 SEASON AT A GLANCE: Price averages 11.6 yards every time he carries the ball, 
nearly three yards better than the next-best average per carry among running 
backs in the Valley area. Price (6-foot-1, 215 pounds), has rushed for 1,466 
