to fuel the Spartans' 46-0 rout of University in a first-round game of the City 
Section Division 4-A playoffs. Price, who also starts at defensive back, 
recovered a fumble on University's first series and scored two plays later on a 
22-yard draw play, carrying two defenders the final five yards. 
