<P>
 Manuel Alvarez Solano's thumb has pointed police to suspects in his slaying, 
18 years after his body was found. 
</P>
<P>
 The sheriff's office Monday said two people have been arrested and a third is 
being sought in the shotgun slaying of the Cuban-born drug dealer. 
</P>
