<HEADLINE>
<P>
FHP CERTIFIED TO OFFER WORKERS' COMP INSURANCE 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 FHP Life Insurance Co. has been designated as one of California's first two 
health maintenance organizations to be certified by the California Department 
of Industrial Relations as a health care organization.The other is Manhattan 
Beach-based Travelers Insurance Co. 
</P>
<P>
 The certification allows both companies to provide workers' compensation 
insurance in a managed care structure, which is aimed at controlling the high 
cost of such insurance.  
</P>
<P>
 It is also meant to simplify the work for employers who are given the option 
of contracting with one company for medical and workers' compensation coverage. 
</P>
